Poll one wp plug-in is simple Ajax based pool plug-in for WordPress. using this plug-in we can customize the pool in the website widget. In the admin we have option to create the pool with maximum six answer. also have option to set start and end date of the pool. In the front end it will display one pool at a time also we can set random pool displ
